GNU General Public License for more details.

Author: Arturo Casal

This a daemon which allows you to run a script every time the button
is pushed.
Supported device: ( 0x1130, 0x0202 ) or sku.23789 (DealExtreme)

 Usage
-------

./panicbutton script.sh

 License
